title: Brooklyn Beckham Throws It Way Back in Adorable Pic With Dad David From His Parents' Wedding Day
text: Brooklyn Beckham Throws It Way Back in Adorable Pic With Dad David From His Parents' Wedding Day by Alex Ungerman 5:54   Playing Brooklyn Beckham Throws It Way Back in Adorable Pic With Dad David From His Parents' Wedding Day Wow. Time really does fly! Brooklyn Beckham proved that on Wednesday, when he shared an adorable pic with dad David Beckham on his parents’ 1999 wedding day when the now-17-year-old was just a baby! ❤❤ A photo posted by bb (@brooklynbeckham) on Feb 8, 2017 at 4:24am PST WATCH: Brooklyn Beckham Shares The Sweetest Dad Moment Between David and Harper The sweet father-son duo sported all-white attire for the big day, while David rocked a so-perfectly ‘90s blond-tipped brushed over 'do. Of course, the Beckham family is not at a loss for adorable moments with each other, as evidenced by David's recent heartwarming snap with daughter Harper. Watch the video below.
